    // The program begins...

    // The program makes this: A function that, after 1 second,
    // will &#39;execute&#39; (i.e. &#39;call&#39;, with parentheses) its argument, resolveWithValue,
    // supplying &#39;Hello World!&#39; as an argument to THAT execution.
